---
title: Sri Lankan-Spiced Lentil, Chicken & Veggie Soup with Yoghurt & Cheesy Garlic Flatbreads
description: Having all the flavours and textures of veggies, chicken, lentils and spices melting into one delectable soup is the perfect way to finish off a day. Enjoy by dipping the
cheesy flatbreads in the soup to soak it up.
